Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}秘立蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是本着“恶之宽宏善之狭隘”的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以培育非法忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是恶忍为目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藏身于黑暗中的教育机构
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又得集合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道又要去找半藏学院那帮人麻烦么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那种半吊子的任务真提不起兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起！对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这样连下忍都当不上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别说下忍了 赶紧退学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未来居然会对他人好言相待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不觉得给她的希望越大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}绝望也就越大么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}依旧这么坏心眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女子学园校规 第四十八条
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本学园以“下克上”为宗旨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上忍在任何情况下都有义务接受下忍的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很赞赏你的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但在那之前你应该先秤一下自己的斤两
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我最近真是愠恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咏同学 又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近蔬菜的价钱不断上涨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听你这么一说好像有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些卖给富人的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}涨了就涨了 我也无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是就连庶民之友的低价豆芽菜都涨价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是想怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你有认真在听么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}时间差不多到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 日影同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豆芽菜的话题还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 日影同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:18.18,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起豆芽菜 迟到了被骂更遭殃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豆芽菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}召集你们来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又有新的任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新的…
Comment: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:33.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校准帧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:40.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:59.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}暗雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:09.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:20.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:27.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:33.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:46.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:51.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON'T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:40.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:59.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:09.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:20.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:27.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:33.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.89,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:46.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:51.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
